# Fennec patch series
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Patches are applied in order by `fennec patch apply`.
# Lines beginning with # are comments. Blank lines are ignored.
#
# SECTION CONVENTION:
#   core/ungoogled-chromium/  — populated by `fennec bootstrap` from upstream
#   core/iridium/             — populated by `fennec bootstrap` from upstream
#   vendor/fennec/            — checked into this repo; edit these directly
#
# core/ patches are NOT present in the repo on a fresh clone.
# Run `fennec bootstrap` to fetch them. Use --skip-core in CI pre-bootstrap.
#
# ADDING A PATCH:
#   fennec patch new <name> --section <section>
#   Then edit the scaffolded file and append it to the correct section below.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

